=========================================================================

This software is a traffic generator for the BSV transaction sharding
pipeline. It emits configurable streams of BRC-124 transaction frames,
BRC-127 subtree group announcements, BRC-131 block announcements,
BRC-132 subtree data frames, and BRC-134 anchor transactions over UDP
or TCP for load and functional testing.

=========================================================================
Conceptual Attribution

The IPv6 multicast transaction broadcast architecture from which this
software draws inspiration was articulated by Dr. Craig S. Wright:

  Multicast within Multicast: Anycast
  https://singulargrit.substack.com/p/multicast-within-multicast-anycast
  https://singulargrit.substack.com/

=========================================================================
Third-Party Standards

This software emits wire-frame formats conforming to BRC-12 and
BRC-124 (and related companions BRC-127, BRC-131, BRC-132, BRC-134),
published standards maintained by BSV Blockchain:

  BRC-12: Raw Transaction Format
  BRC-124: Multicast Frame Format
  BSV Blockchain Standards Repository
  https://github.com/bitcoin-sv/BRCs/

